{"tid":2037360,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"投機者全盤押注港元大幅貶值","createTime":"2020-05-27T02:50:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T05:20:04.000Z","uid":28114,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ec20b5683a976f8f6d08431e685b4c40158cbea6","tid":2037360,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s4.cdn.bb.bbwc.cn/issue_1454/articles/180091719/2020/0526/5ecc87c386121_640x427.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs4.cdn.bb.bbwc.cn%2Fissue_1454%2Farticles%2F180091719%2F2020%2F0526%2F5ecc87c386121_640x427.jpg&h=75a2521b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外匯市場上隨處可見資本可能逃離香港的擔憂，考驗著港元應對經濟衰退的抗壓能力。<br />\n<br />\n投機者通過衍生品全盤押注港元大幅貶值，造成一項看跌指標接近年內最高水準。港元期權成交量上週五飆升至37億美元，其中三分之一押注港元將觸及或跌破兌換保證區間的弱端。<br />\n市場動盪還會惡化這一看法在互換市場上也很明顯，港元與美元互換利差達到1990年代的水準。一年期遠期點收盤價觸及1999年以來最高水準，表明對沖港元貶值的需求激增。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s3.cdn.bb.bbwc.cn/issue_1454/articles/180091719/2020/0526/5ecc87dc9162f_640x359.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs3.cdn.bb.bbwc.cn%2Fissue_1454%2Farticles%2F180091719%2F2020%2F0526%2F5ecc87dc9162f_640x359.png&h=8886c225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上周中國出人意料地決定宣布香港國安立法後，香港成為中美之爭加劇的風暴中心。港元由此創下六周最大跌幅，香港股市也創下2008年以來的最大跌幅。特朗普政府正在考慮應對措施，可能包括撤銷香港的特殊貿易地位，這一風險將削弱香港作為全球金融中心的地位。（撰文：Tian Chen、Kari Soo Lindberg）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.bbwc.cn/1y1511.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.bbwc.cn%2F1y1511.html&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=e0357d4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.bbwc.cn/1y1511.html</a>"},{"pid":"477f623bacc50050ea0108d223109e7c0fc0e968","tid":2037360,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:50:56.000Z","msg":"索羅斯呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c3262a9174c3fc1a0432e38cfa74ade40c7a47c","tid":2037360,"uid":46587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T